 {"id":"brenner_bot-t62l.3","title":"Task: Capture integration tests (stdout/stderr + timeout + provenance)","description":"# Goal
Add tests that verify experiment capture is reliable and deterministic.

---

# Must-test behaviors
- Wrapper-run captures stdout and stderr
- Exit code is recorded correctly
- Timeout kills the process and is recorded
- Provenance fields are populated (cwd, command, timestamps)

---

# Suggested test commands
- `echo "hello"` → stdout capture
- A command that writes to stderr and exits non-zero → stderr + exit code
- A command that sleeps longer than timeout → timeout path

---

# Acceptance criteria
- [ ] Tests are deterministic and fast
- [ ] Tests run in CI (no external dependencies)
